{
  "stem": "21482.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was such-- you know, there was so much killing in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, my father had a very good friend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His name was Rudy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father used to play cards with him all the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one day, my father came running home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "His friend Rudy was shot in front of the hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think he was working there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no reason.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no reason.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There was never a reason to, to kill anybody-- just because we were in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother's parents [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was the last selection.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And again, I don't know anything for sure.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my mother and I-- we never talked about it after the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then when I was ready to ask questions, my mother was already gone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was nobody for me to ask questions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But one day during a selection, I was told to take-- to go downstairs with my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, we didn't live in the same building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My grandparents came to the building where we lived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were told to hide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My mother told me-- my mother and her younger sister-- we lived in an old building.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was like a block, because the entrance to the front was on the side that was already outside of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we had-- so of course, it was locked-- boarded, couldn't use it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The, the back of it was connected with the street behind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it had a big courtyard, huge courtyard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was all-- there was big bushes and big trees.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my grandfather and my grandmother and myself, we laid down under the bushes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My mother and her sister covered us with leaves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they left.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
